# External Integrations

## Clerk
- Used for authentication and user management
- Handle sign-in and sign-up flows
- Implement proper webhook handlers for authentication events
- Follow Clerk's best practices for Next.js 15+ integration

## Apify
- Used for scraping Crexi commercial real estate listings
- Implement proper error handling for Apify client requests
- Cache responses where appropriate to improve performance
- Respect rate limits and implement retry logic
- Monitor scraping jobs and handle failures gracefully

## Supabase
- Database for storing user data and search history
- Follow migration conventions for database schema changes
- Use prepared statements to prevent SQL injection
- Implement proper error handling for database operations

## Other Services
- Ensure environment variables are properly configured for all third-party services
- Document required environment variables in .env.example
- Keep API keys and secrets secure
- Handle service outages gracefully with appropriate fallbacks
